sentences: The Quiet Room were a progressive metal band signed to Metal Blade from 1992 to 2003.
They released two demos from 1993-1995 before releasing their debut album through an indie label in 1997.
In 1999, they signed with Metal Blade and their debut album was re-released that same year.
In 2000, they released their second album, Reconceive.
After their second album, they released a demo in 2002.
Negative Four lasted two years with an album recorded but not released in 2004.
